Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:09.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kagami Yoshimizu Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ambiguous 3cm?\NDoes that mean it's plushy? Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wrapping is a uniform, argh,\Nit's not an act, pooh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta do your best, gotta just do it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's time to catch 'n' release, eek{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Between sweat (whoop)\NSweat (whoop){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darlin', darlin', freeze! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kinda lethargic,\Nsomething's kinda comin' out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you... Oh wait,\None of those was different{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worrywarts, high metal bars {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tasty thoughts... And that's enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The heated body of that\Nflying you-know-who{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's what you call a normal girlie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I the only one surprised? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seconds on pork-bone broth ramen\Nwith wire-hard noodles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Da da da da da {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pom-poms cheer squad{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's get cherry pie {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy fun welcoming party {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look up! Sensation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah! Feeling of existence,\Ndot dot small planet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:00:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Collided and it melted away,\Nin total awe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go all out to sing, shi-ranger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take it away! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should be the one who'll be\Nlaughing in the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I have the sailor suit\N← This is my conclusion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's only Monday! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Already in a bad mood? What to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really prefer the summer outfits\N← kya! Wah! Good! (cute!) < 3{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until we approach 3 pixels,\Nno hesitations please ★{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do your best, be energetic {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My darlin', darlin' please! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw a shooting star the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Kagami said,\N"Realistically speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,chanting a wish\Nthree times is impossible."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shooting star? How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've rarely seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see that many stars\Nfrom my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your house is in\Ndowntown Tokyo, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'd just watch it\Nwith fascination,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and be unable to recite a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing wonderful,\Nbrightly shining stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:02:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one gets a feeling of happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps that is why the legend goes\Nthat your wishes come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are just so straightforward...\NIt's blinding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Various Ways to Spend Christmas Eve"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost winter vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though we have finals before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys have any plans\Nfor winter vacation, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nwe haven't traveled at all lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to Asakusa the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? When did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.72,0:02:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trains in the winter\Nmake you drowsy, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She slept past her destination?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... But isn't that in\Nthe opposite direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, I slept too long,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it doubled back from the final stop,\Nand I slept past my station again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I came to, it was Asakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, there's a limit on\Noversleeping for your destination...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But oversleeping your destination\Nisn't a completely bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to take a short trip\Nto Asakusa as a result, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's not something\Nto be doing during your exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought for a moment that a girl\Nin a sailor outfit had a machine gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and passed by the platform\Nfor a fleeting moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to say that it was\Na raid or something, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they say that children who sleep\Nare the ones that grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you grow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this one's even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad, when he went to deliver\Nhis script after an all-nighter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,got on an early train, overslept\Nall the way to the final stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--For real?!\N--then the train made a U-turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and before he knew it,\Nhe had overslept again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went back and forth many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He woke up closer and closer \Nto the destination station,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:33.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Look, Patrasche... That's \Na painting by Rubens...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--but he would always sleep past \Nit by a very close margin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was so tired that he just\Nwanted to come home and sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he couldn't manage\Nto make his way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the end, when\Nhe woke up with a start,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he couldn't figure out which direction\Nhe was heading at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I fall asleep, I always\Nwake up before my station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing...\NI wonder how you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's an alarm clock\Ninstalled inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though the clock in her stomach\Nseems to be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:03:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always eating tons of sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when the train or the seats\Nare warm, you get really sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. It's just like\Na sunny winter afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you're drowsing off in the\Nwindow side seat of your classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warm and comfy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are these comrades\Ncovering for each other now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, when I woke\Nher up on the train home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up! We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five more minutes... Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she said loudly in her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone around us\Nwas laughing at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a friend that\Nsaid that during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, brother, talk about birds\Nof a feather flocking together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? We're the same?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder why it's five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it because it's very upsetting\Nwhen you go wake someone up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they say, "Give me one\Nmore hour," or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you say "five more minutes"\Nabout a lot more than just sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, "Hold on for\Nfive minutes" and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's not too long\Nand not too short.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though five minutes spent waiting\Nfor a train seems really long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in general, the more likely one\Nis to say "five more minutes,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the less likely it's going\Nto be only five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how they say\Nnot to use cell phones
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or put makeup on in the train, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it worse when someone leans\Nup against you, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sometimes they're so heavy\Nthat it's easier to stay standing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even after all the effort\Nyou went through to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when sticky hair from\Nan elderly person comes over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sometimes think, "Go over there!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how many times\Nthey fix their posture,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they always fall over\Nin the same direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right. It's so mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was sleeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this side had a middle-aged man\Nwhile the other was empty,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that I wanted to\Nlean towards the empty space,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I always end up leaning\Ntowards the middle-aged man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's a direction that's\Neasier for you to lean, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the person next to me\Nfalls over towards me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shrink in on myself like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I do, their elbows\Nstart hitting my sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think they're actually\Nawake when they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In our school, you know how\Nsome people take the up train
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and some take the down train?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that the up people are\Nmore refined than the down people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-{\i1}chan {\i0}is an up person, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Surely not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, let us head back\Nto the borderlands, all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, I have another station left...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S'up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't study at all last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand,\NI'm pretty psyched this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though I hate to say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much were you able to study?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Four whole hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Only four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, you do everything\Nso carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is just between us,\Nbut I do study quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that you have\Na competitive streak, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in the end, I have the pride\Nof being the older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling that I had to stay a step\Nahead of Tsukasa was very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, I say that older\Nor younger doesn't matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I used to think about it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wasn't Tsukasa a very\Ndisappointing opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you've got no right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this\Nyear's present will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you still get presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, how long did\Nyou believe in Santa Claus?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Santa Claus doesn't really exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s house\NSanta never swung by,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so her dad was giving her\Npresents in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she thought that he really\Nwas out there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old man really wants to show\Noff to his daughter, doesn't he...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hiiragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hiiragi, this is the printout\Nfrom the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Hiiragi-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiiragi, you dropped\Nyour mechanical pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami-{\i1}san{\i0}, this is the printout\Nfrom the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sebastian was so smelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, you dropped\Nyour handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, maybe I'm dropping by\NTsukasa's class a bit too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, my cavity has\Nbeen starting to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... Don't you hate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate dentists too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you went to go\Nfix a cavity the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentists always take\Na while to treat a tooth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when they're done with one,\Nthey find another tooth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and so it takes quite\Na bit of time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I couldn't help but run away,\Ngiving all sorts of reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's saying it so cutely,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but isn't she doing\Nsomething drastic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how about we all get together\Nfor a Christmas bash?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. I already have\Nsomething to do on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what?\NSomething involving a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have plans to go out\Nwith your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told Dad that\NI was going to be out late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're really going\Non a date with a boyfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to burst your bubble,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's just a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, I'm not lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because most of\Nthe customers are guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you had snuck ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a limited-time\Nevent for Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where we all dress up\Nlike Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like that kind\Nof stuff, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you guys cosplay as shrine maidens\Nfor New Year's, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At your family shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call it cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Santa... It's a good thing\Nthat he gives out presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's totally breaking and entering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, I thought so\Nwhen I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't insult the roots of\Na saint's existence that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a disgusting kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa is someone that\Ngives dreams out to kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of men seek their dreams\Nfrom a shrimp like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Isn't she insulting me\Nvery nonchalantly here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can you guys celebrate\NChristmas in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, we got\NChristmas presents very normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We enshrine the myriad deities\Nat our place,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we go pay homage to temples\Nlike everyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ Joy to the world, the Lord is... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--and we've even sung hymns in a church.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... That's just so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, but our older sister, a shrine maiden,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:10:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,said that she wanted to\Nget married in a wedding dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it gets that far,\Ndoesn't it get a bit complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo! It's getting cold lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sis. Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective drama show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.\NI'm just watching it on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, I get it! That guy did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are strange things\Nabout this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't anything strange\Nabout it! This solves the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, you're not\Ninvolved in any of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, this is why\Nthe cops are no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're one of those cops, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I getting a phone call now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost at the point\Nwhere the culprit confesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you were the one that did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no choice,\Nif you've already found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do all these 2-hour drama shows\Nend at the top of a cliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:12:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe people can't decide to\Ngo through with something
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless they're pushed to the edge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo! You doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evenin', Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The movie spin-off of\Na popular cop drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad rented it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The case doesn't happen\Nin a boardroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happens at the crime scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, there's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such passionate turns\Nof events never happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the point you deny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the thief wasn't the guy\Nwho stole the receipt,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but someone who was sent out\Nby the police chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why police chiefs...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something rings a bell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, on cop shows, they\Ngive cutlet bowls to suspects,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I heard they can't\Ndo that in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's all fiction,\Nso there are a lot of lies in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the Metropolitan Police Chief
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't actually have\Nthat many grandkids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Metropolitan Police\NChief's grandkids?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen any as such...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like Mai to exist,\Nat least, as a glimmer of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an empty wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of cases where\Nadults go after children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make kids learn martial arts,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stuff like that will happen less often.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that Mr. Oyama,\Nafter intense training,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was able to defeat a cow\Nwith one barehanded blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also hear that his daily workout\Nis defeating twenty bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even then, after a while,\Nwon't you go back to square one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When those kids grow up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll be stronger as adults too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, it's, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you practice martial arts,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they say you grow up with\Na straightforward heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone with a twisted mind\Ndespite practicing martial arts
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is right in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Yui has a younger sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I have a cousin that will be\Nentering high school next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--She was born really frail, but is\Nhonest, pure, and really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Konata-{\i1}oneechan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But going by the "healthy soul\Nresides in a healthy body" theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those pretty eyes of hers\Nsuddenly start looking like
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,scheming ones that are\Nhiding something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think everything goes\Nexactly like in the proverbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're a prime example.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year is almost over already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time December comes around,\NI feel like the year flew by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you guys going\Nto be shrine maidens
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to help your family out\Nagain, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come pick your fortunes\Nand stuff again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About fortunes...\NWhen you pick an "Unlucky" result,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you get a bad feeling\Nfrom its negative image,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when you pick "Great Blessings",
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you feel like you've\Nwasted your luck so early on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they do say "Average Blessings"\Nis the best fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, this is an early present\Nfrom your teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm handing out report cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here. Thanks for all the hard studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, how'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, I don't need\Npresents like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my policy as Santa\Nto give you all points
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,according to how hard\Nyou've worked as presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy it. It comes with a bonus gift:\NWinter vacation homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of Christmas cake\Nwould you like this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you go to a cake shop,\Nthere are so many cute cakes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:15:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that just looking at them is very fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happens to the\Nleftover cakes after Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the employees\Ntake them home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if nobody decided\Nto take them home,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe they throw\Nthem away after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They often relate the prime\Nmarriage age to Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're both "until the 25th".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas cakes are ordinary\Ncakes after the 25th,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when the night ends,\Ndecorated cakes suddenly pale,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you don't feel like\Neating them at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking about Santa with\NKona-{\i1}chan {\i0}the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}, how long did\Nyou believe in Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like you believed it\Nfor a long time, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed in Santa in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I wanted to\Nwrite a letter of thanks to Santa,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I looked it up in\Nall sorts of places.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since asking both my parents\Ndidn't lead to any answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked it up more carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I came across phrases like
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stories that Santa Claus was\Nbased on" and "Origin of Santa,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so my dreams were shattered\Npretty early on in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:05.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Report Card"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, how'd you do? Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ever come up\Nwith something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's somehow a bit frustrating\Nthat I'm losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-{\i1}chan {\i0}is always at\Nthe top of our class,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People like us would never win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't care about grades at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, like breast size. Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting a bit hungry...\NI guess I'll have some cup ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These three minutes spent waiting\Nseem like an awfully long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this to pass the time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever done that, and made your\Nnoodles all soggy and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Like with fried noodles in a cup,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it soaks up all the hot water\Nand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that she was going to be late,\Nbut this is a bit too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hate to see this as a habit,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I have to be stern every so often,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:16:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what time do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Christmas present\Nfrom me to you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be cold after staying out\Nso late. Want some hot tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! I'll have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad is so happy that he just might die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Yui is in the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, you reek of alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drunk driving is not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a bit to drink around here\Nafter I parked my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me! It's Christmas Eve,\Nyet my husband is out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were planning to\Nspend it alone together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, why not drop in on your folks\Ninstead of us for once...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello, Yui? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on surprising you\Nby sneaking home,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the door was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you at your parents' place now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go home at top speed right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring the signals and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, you shouldn't\Ngo breaking the law...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had my breather,\Nso I think I'll log in for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, our teacher's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, let's have a riot.\NOf course, until morning... There.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hold on one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Christmas cakes - 50% off"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not leftovers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not leftovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nanako Kuroi - 27 years old"\N"Single"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I bought it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here last Sunday too,\Nto buy some manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you'd shell out the\Ntransportation costs to swing by...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I know it's for the points,\Nyou really go pretty far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, do you use the\Nitems you get from stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't use any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can understand. It's hard\Nto use stuff like that, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. It's such a waste\Nto use it that I can't use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because using it depreciates its value.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh...\NThat's how you approach it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you get that static shock thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Konata is always\Nsitting in front of the computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe strange electric waves\Nalready fill her body or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you really hate winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear there are times\Nthat you can get shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by touching other people's hands, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:19.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ouch, ouch, ouch, ouch, ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Maybe these two actually don't \Nget along with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wanted to see it\None more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning Luckies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akira Kogami, your navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time passes by so quickly that {\i1}Lucky\NChannel {\i0}is already in episode eleven!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on that eleventh episode,\NI am finally able to relay to you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,news that you've all been\Nwaiting so long for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Until now, there were so many\Npassionate voices sent to us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:55.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--She's not listening at \Nall today, as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--from fans asking, "We'd \Nabsolutely, positively like to see
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Miss Akira in the main\Nsegment as well!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:03.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hello. I'm the assistant, \NMinoru Shiraishi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--And in the next episode, I, Akira Kogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm going to make an appearance \Nin the main segment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:06.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--But my intro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Konata Izumi from Saitama,\Nwho sent a postcard to Newtype,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone else,\Nthank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you have been cast\Nas well, Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what's with that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're finally showing up in the\Nmain segment in episode 12?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I was in the main segment so long\Nago, hmph!" way of putting it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that! I'm honored\Nthat I can act along with you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the main segment\Nas well, Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you say you've\Nbeen in the main segment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all you did this time was\Npick up a handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you start thinking,\N"Maybe I can make it in this industry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is when you're the most vulnerable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that, if you don't\Nwant to be gone too quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll engrave it into my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I can't wait for the next episode\Nif I hear news like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Air it right now, please! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is trembling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, anxious to watch,\Nalready standing by naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, let's air it right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:21:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to answer all the feelings of the\Ndear fans, instead of holding out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Can't we do something \Nabout a 30-minute block?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:04.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well, all things considered, isn't \Nsomething like that impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm asking, pretty please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll end it here after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, keep sending messages for me\Nto the radio show or our homepage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-nee...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be bad to stand out\Nmore than the main characters...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been many cases\Nwhere a friend or nemesis,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone other than the main\Ncharacter, ended up more popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}?\NIs something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you're popular lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you getting full of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:35.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, no, no, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't you think they'll \Nmake action figures of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, no, no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't you think you can win first \Nplace in the popularity poll?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:39.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop kidding with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:42.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--There's no way that would \Nhappen. Stop and listen for--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is Tsukasa and\NMiyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}'s duet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}, let's sing up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange that you'd pick a song for\NTsukasa and Miyuki to sing, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have proper knowledge\Nof all sorts of songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an anime song after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this, anime songs\Ncome in handy, amazingly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.68,0:22:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ This sort of thing is good,\NI wish I could do it ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Dreams like that, dreams like this,\Nthere are so many ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ All, all, all, he will grant them all ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ He grants them with\Na mysterious pocket ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.55,0:22:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I want to fly through the skies ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.45,0:22:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Here, have a Bamboo-Copter! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bad impersonation!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Ah, ah, ah, I love Doraemon so much! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.48,0:23:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Homework, school duty... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:16.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.32,0:23:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's with the\Nnext episode of {\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.48,0:23:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the other day, I got\Nreally hungry late at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since it was so late,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered whether I should\Neat something or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that a little bit wouldn't hurt,\Nso I chose to go eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I went to the kitchen,\Nand opened the fridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thinking I recalled there being\Na couple leftover sweets from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Is it that time already?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.45,0:23:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Let's Go to the Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:43.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's Go to the Festival"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to it!
